<task id="053" project="sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix">
  <metadata>
    <title>Outcome E grep acceptance (FR-E2)</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>15 minutes</estimated-effort>
    <assigned>AI agent</assigned>
    <tags>bff-api, outcome-e, acceptance, phase-4</tags>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Sequential acceptance check after migration verification</parallel-reason>
    <rigor>STANDARD</rigor>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Run the FR-E2 acceptance greps. Confirm zero direct `IOpenAiClient` / `IPlaybookService` references outside `Services/Ai/`.
  </prompt>

  <role>.NET acceptance verifier.</role>
  <goal>Greps return zero outside Services/Ai/; results captured in EXECUTION-LOG.md.</goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="src">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/</file>
    <file purpose="spec">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/spec.md</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec.md FR-E2">grep returns 0 outside Services/Ai/</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/spec.md</file>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/CLAUDE.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>Per FR-E2 acceptance: `grep -r "IOpenAiClient\|IPlaybookService" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/{Finance,Workspace,Jobs,Dataverse}/` returns 0; `grep -r "Sprk.Bff.Api.Services.Ai\." src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/{Finance,Workspace,Dataverse}/` returns only `PublicContracts` references.</background>
    <dependencies><dependency task="052" status="not-started">Test verification stable</dependency></dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">`grep -r "IOpenAiClient\|IPlaybookService" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/{Finance,Workspace,Jobs,Dataverse}/` — must return 0 (Jobs excluding the relocated handlers which are now at Services/Ai/Jobs/)</step>
    <step order="2">`grep -r "IOpenAiClient\|IPlaybookService" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Filters/` — must return 0</step>
    <step order="3">`grep -r "Sprk.Bff.Api.Services.Ai\." src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/{Finance,Workspace,Dataverse}/` — must return only `PublicContracts` references</step>
    <step order="4">Capture all grep outputs in EXECUTION-LOG.md</step>
    <step order="5">If any fail: identify the consumer; either migrate or document justification (e.g., "internal AI helper that legitimately needs raw client")</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX.md</step>
  </steps>

  <tools><tool name="git">grep</tool></tools>

  <outputs><output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/EXECUTION-LOG.md (acceptance grep results)</output></outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">grep #1 returns 0 (or documented exceptions)</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">grep #2 returns 0</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">grep #3 returns only PublicContracts references</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
